channel.title: Safe Computer (beta stage) and My new music player! i need beta testers!
channel.description:
Safe computer is a device for keeping small children and pesky annoyances away from your computer, IT MAY NOT WORK WITH ALL COMPUTERS!!!!!!!!! if it doesn't send me a pic of any errors or size problems.
The Media players both accept files from your computer and the internet as the url. here are some example urls (they actually work) all music is by three days grace. [code]http://www.riggallery.com/bah/grizzle/05-The%20Good%20Life.mp3 http://www.riggallery.com/bah/grizzle/09-Bully.mp3 http://www.riggallery.com/bah/grizzle/10-Without%20You.mp3 http://miso.zoomshare.com/files/Three_Days_Grace_-_Break.mp3[/code]
instructions for "Safe computer"
To exit safe computer there is a small button right beside the "start" menu. Click this button and it will enable the moderator panel, use the mod panel to get out.
The media player should just be a peice of cake for all you coding fags out there. Dl links: http://uppit.com/v/OC5UH23N - fallout media player http://uppit.com/v/10a2j3gt - mike's media player v1 http://uppit.com/v/C1N0U2J6 - safe computer
